          <p id="IO-UN.1191">OHCHR is the focal point for UN human rights activities, with a mandate to promote and protect all human rights for all people. It is guided by relevant resolutions of the General Assembly, the UN Charter, the 1948 Universal Declaration of Human Rights and subsequent human rights instruments, the Vienna Declaration and programme of action adopted by the 1993 World Conference on Human Rights, and the outcome document of the 2005 World Summit of the General Assembly.</p>
     </int-org-block>
     <int-org-section id="IO-UN.1192" sllink="SLSDOC" slsdocrf="INT-ORG-SECTREF">
